'''''Star Wars Insider'' 68''' is the sixty-eighth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine. It was released to newsstands on [[June 3]], [[2003]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"From the Editor's Desk"
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Star News]]" {{C|by [[Kevin Rubio]], [[Mary Franklin]], [[Benjamin Harper]]}}
*"[[Toy Box]]" &mdash; Year of the Clone {{C|by Andy@Hasbro}}
*"[[Behind the Magic]]" &mdash; Carbon Copies {{C|by [[Rob Coleman]]}}
*"[[HoloNet News (Insider)|HoloNet News]]" {{C|by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]}}
**"[[Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 14:7:02]]"
**"[[CIS Shadowfeed Dispatch 14:7:01 Edition]]"
*"[[Gamescape]]"
**[[Hero's Guide|Hero's Journey]] {{C|by [[Gary M. Sarli]]}}
**''Star Wars'' Galaxies Update {{C|by [[W. Haden Blackman]]}}
*"[[Bookshelf]]" &mdash; [[Shatterpoint (novel)|Welcome to the Jungle]] {{C|by [[Jason Fry]]}}
*"[[Comics Link]]" &mdash; The Clone Wars, Year Two {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*"[[Set Piece]]" &mdash; Mos Eisley Spaceport Docking Bay 94 {{C|by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" &mdash; It's the End of Toy Fair {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet|Steve Sansweet]]}}
*"[[Crossword (department)|Crossword]]" &mdash; For Members Only {{C|by [[Michael Selinker]]}}
*"[[Star Wars Q&A|''Star Wars'' Q&A'']] {{C|by Pablo Hidalgo}}
*"[[The Last Page]]" {{C|by [[Tony Moseley]]}}

===Features===
*"[[Prequel Update]]" {{C|by [[Dave Gross]]}}
*:<small>Producer [[Rick McCallum]] knocks down rumors, sets a date for shooting, and tells exactly how much of the [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|Episode III]] script [[George Lucas]] has turned over.</small>
*"[[Cartoon Guru]]" {{C|by [[Eric Moro]]}}
*:<small>What do a boy genius, three preschool super heroins, and a time-traveling samurai have to do with ''Star Wars''? [[Cartoon Network]]'s [[Star Wars: Clone Wars|''Clone Wars'']] director [[Genndy Tartakovsky]].</small>
*"[[Beyond the Storyboard: Dan Gregoire on Pre-Visualising Episode II]]" {{C|by [[Ron Magid]]}}
*:<small>Previsulization is not just a really long word; it's what [[Daniel D. Gregoire|Dan Gregoire]] does best.</small>
*"[[Carrie on... Star Wars, Celebrity & the Art of Conversation|Carrie on... ''Star Wars'', Celebrity & the Art of Conversation]]" {{C|by [[Christopher Cerasi]]}}
*:<small>''Star Wars Insider'' talks to [[Carrie Fisher|the brains behind the buns]].</small>
*"[[Poster Perfect: Painting a Thousand Words]]" {{C|by [[William Plumb]]}}
*:<small>Retrace the history of a select few ''Star Wars'' posters through the ages.</small>
*"[[Vision Quest: The Origins of the Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections|Vision Quest: The Origins of the ''Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections'']]" {{C|by [[David West Reynolds (real person)|David West Reynolds]]}}
*:<small>An inside look at [[Dorling Kindersley|DK Publishing's]] ''[[Star Wars: Incredible Cross-Sections]]''.</small>
*"[[Tattoo Detoo]]" {{C|by [[Shane Turgeon]]}}
*:<small>''Star Wars'' fans leave their mark on society.</small>
*"[[Hero of Cartao]]: Episode I Hero's Call" {{C|by [[Timothy Zahn]]}}
*:<small>The world of [[Cartao/Legends|Cartao]], home of [[Spaarti Creations]], sits near the front lines of the galaxy-wide [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Neither the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] nor the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] have shown an interest–until now.</small>

